name: ARGHTEE - HYPE YOUR NFT Gif Loop by STEPHEN HUTCHINS
description: Collaboration between the NFT Hypeman "Arghtee" and the maestro himself "Stephen Hutchins". Piece originally planned as use in promotion for the Hypeman in a campaign to onboard more artists to the Tezos Blockchain and "hicetnunc", and for general song awareness for "Hype Your NFT", the NFT song from Arghtee. The GIF loop is the original loop used by Arghtee in the #CleanNFT campaign.
